++ Pretty Options

Options should be pretty in appearance. This means:
    * icons
    * colours
    * [Comparison] tables
    * [Checklist]s

++Examples

Wordpress has a list of roles and capabilities that are differentiated only by text. It is difficult to determine what is best since no effort is made to explain the differences.

wordpress has a list of possible roles and capabilities
 - why is there not a prettified list of them with descriptions?